{"tid":1466911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我有啲嘢一定要同武講","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:04.000Z","uid":150848,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc9263b0b660b5930c0b66fd490013d5ec57ad6","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"呢一番話可以套落所有人身上，無論和理非定勇武，因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未來大家都一定會喺戰場上</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，講到明，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我死咗落地獄都唔割</span></span>，但我今次真係有啲無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日喺機場阻止旅客，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點都唔啱</span></span> ，冇效果之餘，一定會做臭我哋個朵，做錯咗就要認，要反省，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個先係我地勁過popo嘅地方</span></span>，我唔係勇武，但每一次令我最灰心最想割嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔係你哋衝</span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">而係你哋比情緒支配咗，喺唔啱嘅時間衝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明白每個人都有情緒，但呢場運動係屬於每個香港人嘅，每一次想衝嘅時候，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">考慮下可以為每個參與嘅人帶黎啲乜</span></span>，而唔係比個人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嘅仇恨蒙蔽</span></span>，見到有兄弟衝得唔啱應該要制止佢 (唔排除係鬼) 。我知啱唔啱呢啲好主觀，但正因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">每個人諗過先衝</span></span>，咁先唔易比鬼分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而和理非好明顯喺機場呢一仗都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做得未夠好</span></span>，冇好好咁向旅客確切咁傳遞信息，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有啲遊客仲話我哋玩手機，但又真係駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n總言之，經一事，長一智，有啲野做錯咗就返唔到轉頭，我哋要做嘅係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">反省，補救同承認錯誤</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，想同大家講，香港已經進入咗一個新階段，政府手段只會越黎越硬，我哋唔應該再分<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">勇武定和理非，我哋只有香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HongKongers Assemble!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8b00df10337c400f252db40736bc8d01e2284ef6","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3f6f458ab3d55d084e99dfd2d8e0575ca2c3b93f","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9eb1150ece0665c62b86d830c96e7aad42914026","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1dea07d1e6cbf0877663a8a3757f7d8cdde48ad1","tid":1466911,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:07.000Z","msg":"藍絲夠話個女仔係比示威者射盲 打佢既示威者係警察扮好出奇？ 你有見藍絲會割警察席嗎？"},{"pid":"fe55bc0ddbd61259d66df914fa875a5c0e45459f","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ea02d927204b1c33b5d4a0985e2d34f8c4410eb3","tid":1466911,"uid":3255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"自己反醒 改進<br />\n<br />\n唔駛互屌<br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"bd45eb1091ff747a1aa050649ed7a002208ec86a","tid":1466911,"uid":89105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n香港人會繼續進步"},{"pid":"9eaa09a7764b2210a21c297cee285b08be7f970c","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dea07d1e6cbf0877663a8a3757f7d8cdde48ad1","tid":1466911,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:07.000Z","msg":"藍絲夠話個女仔係比示威者射盲 打佢既示威者係警察扮好出奇？ 你有見藍絲會割警察席嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:11.000Z","msg":"我邊度有話割...我係話我哋做錯咗就要反省，如果唔係同popo有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2ddb0a6e8cb81b06fc41ad113aef77cfe41ef1","tid":1466911,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"［文宣煲大佢］有疑似黑社會入機場踩線搞恐襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地已經冇可能再割蓆"},{"pid":"820494e5e49848c24d0ca8751ba34c572695b9df","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea02d927204b1c33b5d4a0985e2d34f8c4410eb3","tid":1466911,"uid":3255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"自己反醒 改進<br />\n<br />\n唔駛互屌<br />\n<br />\n加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:59.000Z","msg":"唔係互屌，我分人都好火爆，好明白有時嬲係真係要人點醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e91e185d1cbf1f4ea0c7b1f6103cad78ebe9a5","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ce683cde6e22bd9b33bff410643bbcc71602e6e0","tid":1466911,"uid":260088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"道歉大行動，你我有責<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民間記者會要AM開，先道歉，多次，先壓住輿論</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3日唔入機場，唔係輸曬外媒<br />\n而且而家文宣需要大量人手<br />\n3日唔入機場，睇左風向壓唔壓得住先<br />\n星期六仲要保護老師，對付福建幫"},{"pid":"57241e6706d7271e881750cc81023967834da4dc","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9edd215e20b7c3c91ce3fa862171a6440df80032","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce683cde6e22bd9b33bff410643bbcc71602e6e0","tid":1466911,"uid":260088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"道歉大行動，你我有責<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民間記者會要AM開，先道歉，多次，先壓住輿論</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3日唔入機場，唔係輸曬外媒<br />\n而且而家文宣需要大量人手<br />\n3日唔入機場，睇左風向壓唔壓得住先<br />\n星期六仲要保護老師，對付福建幫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:29.000Z","msg":"都同意，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef48fbf81f828c2f4cb7fdf0ce0d1f6e1c9fde9a","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c57e7a044d0d046a8f6ef45dbd6151377199603","tid":1466911,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同<br />\n<br />\n雖然仇警情緒已經入晒血，而狗亦都專登同你講我放鬼入黎等你互鬥。<br />\n做野冷靜為首要考慮，事情已變事實，割唔割亦都唔洗討論，大家向前望就得。"},{"pid":"c8b0a146f8f7ab656b84acc0f18c27c394da258f","tid":1466911,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"我以為你講公安同阻警車單嘢<br />\n塞離境嗰班未必係勇武派<br />\n可能只係和理非同勇武之間嗰班人...."},{"pid":"5c0125f143e2a9b96c7bea26d73c5b5e9ed12b82","tid":1466911,"uid":295761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"［請廣傳］818民陣遊行係極為重要既關鍵一戰<br />\n<br />\n當大家焦點去曬機場既時間，大家唔好唔記得818民陣既和理非遊行！呢個遊行係黎緊一場極為重要既民意授權戰！<br />\n<br />\n意義就好似外國政府要推行一項政策遇到障礙時，都會主動提前大選，取得民意授權，先至能夠俾佢繼續推行落去，例如日本首相安倍晉三前年受醜聞困擾，佢提前大選，結果大勝，上個月參議院改選又保住控制權，黎緊就會上國會推修憲令自衛隊變軍隊！ <br />\n但好似英國前首相may姐咁，佢同樣前年提前大選想攞民意推佢個脫歐方案，保住個位但議席輸到九彩，卒之挨唔住要落台，所以818遊行既人數多少，將會直接主宰呢場運動仲可唔可以走落去，所以818輸人，我地就可以收皮。<br />\n<br />\n政府亦都會睇實星期日多唔多人遊行，係風向標，少人既話就會立即全面恢復運作，甚至開turbo照過明日大愚國歌法毫無顧慮。<br />\n<br />\n所有跪求大家瘋狂廣傳，係呢幾日谷盡星期日遊行！"},{"pid":"8d1780712440be676285b9f152caab9aea321cc5","tid":1466911,"uid":198715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"又話唔割又無奈又唔應該<br />\n咁即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"86bbed8b3fbd1fbdfdc18d9ce49309ad04deaff1","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b0a146f8f7ab656b84acc0f18c27c394da258f","tid":1466911,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"我以為你講公安同阻警車單嘢<br />\n塞離境嗰班未必係勇武派<br />\n可能只係和理非同勇武之間嗰班人...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"邊一派都好，一定要諗清楚，如果唔係鬼好易煽動我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12c8fb9cd76ebe78245d3412b211e7cc62dc73c","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d1780712440be676285b9f152caab9aea321cc5","tid":1466911,"uid":198715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"又話唔割又無奈又唔應該<br />\n咁即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"你鐘意隊波輸咗都會唔開心啦，係咪即刻撐另一隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498e7cd4e08f9cf8e756a9a9fce21b04f18c8239","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"862c6068567cd0316624377e095cd937f797dde0","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"91ea55409a64c81408f7b03365b500865591cea4","tid":1466911,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:23.000Z","msg":"push"}]}